structures evolve to a disc-like state despite the strain\neigenvalues sometimes indicating opposite (rod-like) behaviour, as well as\nexplaining vorticity and strain alignments in HIT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Oct 2017 00:30:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-10"}
